
To use our travel app you can follow the steps below:

Step 1: You will prompted to enter you personal details. If they are not a number or incorrect, you will be prompted to re-enter them.
Step 2: You will be given options to select your mode of travel. 
Step 3: You will be given the option to select a date, that must be within 2022-2025, as that is the booking range as of now.
Step 4: *You can choose a city in the North Island, of the options.
Step 5: You will be prompted to enter your payment details.

*if you select intercity bus travel.

That's it!